oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Anna Häussler Weiner
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Dorman family; portraits; Weiner, Anna H.; Weiner family;
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Anna Häussler Weiner (1871-1911) – Born in Mannheim, Germany. Came to America as a cook for Herman Bensdorf at a young age. Married in 1895.
